        "timestamp": "2019-10-31 13:30:42.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 7: Code-Review-2\n\n(1 comment)\n\nA general question: what's the point of upstreaming our internal CI pipeline config? Shouldn't it stay in our internal repo? In it's current shape it's useless for anyone but us.",
        "patchset_number": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "4c5667610aaf5e31aa3458300b9ed337cfe5ef81",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3957,
          "name": "Samuli Silvius",
          "display_name": null,
